# Therapist Website - Dr. Serena Blake, PsyD

This is a fully responsive, accessible, and elegant website built for the internship assignment at [Grow My Therapy](https://growmytherapy.com). The site mirrors the design style of [drjenniferhahm.com](https://www.drjenniferhahm.com/) and is built using **Next.js 14 (App Router)** and **Tailwind CSS**.

